Class
Description
CellCalculationReponseServiceImpl
The CellCalculationReponseServiceImpl class implements the CellCalculationResponseService interface.
CellCalculationRequest
The CellCalculationRequest class represents the request body for cell calculation-related HTTP requests.
CellCalculationRequestService
The CellCalculationRequestService interface defines the contract for services responsible for preprocessing and processing cell calculation requests.
CellCalculationRequestServiceImpl
The CellCalculationRequestServiceImpl class implements the CellCalculationRequestService interface.
CellCalculationResponse
The CellCalculationResponse class represents the response body for cell calculation-related HTTP requests.
CellCalculationResponseService
The CellCalculationResponseService interface defines the contract for services responsible for post-processing cell calculation responses and converting them into the appropriate format represented by CellCalculationResponse.
CellController
The CellController class serves as a Spring MVC controller handling HTTP requests related to cell calculations.
DicBeanStatusController
The DicBeanStatusController class serves as a Spring MVC controller handling HTTP requests related to the status of the DIC bean.
DocBeanStatusController
The DocBeanStatusController class serves as a Spring MVC controller handling HTTP requests related to the status of the DOC bean.
PandoraCalculationRestApi
The main class for starting the PANDORA Calculation Rest API application.
RequestBody
The RequestBody interface defines the contract for request body objects.
RiverController
The RiverController class serves as a Spring MVC controller handling HTTP requests related to river information.
SpeciesController
The SpeciesController class handles HTTP requests related to species information.
SpeciesResponse
The SpeciesResponse class represents the response body for species-related HTTP requests.
SpeciesResponseService
The SpeciesResponseService interface defines the contract for services responsible for post-processing species-related responses and converting them into the appropriate format represented by SpeciesResponse.
SpeciesResponseServiceImpl
The SpeciesResponseServiceImpl class implements the SpeciesResponseService interface.
